addLiquiditySingleAsset(address,string,a.notice: SET MANAGER ONLY. Adds liquidity to an AMM pool for a specified AMM using a single asset if supported.  Differs from addLiquidity as it will opt to use the AMMs single asset liquidity function if it exists User specifies what component and component quantity to contribute and the minimum number of  liquidity pool tokens to receive.
